{% assign housingLubeProduct = all_products[product.metafields.my_fields.recommended_lube_housing] %}

{% assign springLubeProduct = all_products[product.metafields.my_fields.recommended_lube_spring] %}

We recommend <a href="{{ housingLubeProduct.url }}" target="_blank">{{ housingLubeProduct.title }}</a> for the stem and housing, and <a href="{{ springLubeProduct.url }}" target="_blank">{{ springLubeProduct.title }}</a> for the spring.

{%- case product.metafields.my_fields.switch_filming %}
{%- when "Recommended" -%}
&nbsp; We recommend the use of <a href="/collections/switch-films" target="_blank">switch films</a> on this product.
{%- when "Optional" -%}
&nbsp; The tolerances on this switch are generally good, so the use of <a href="/collections/switch-films" target="_blank">switch films</a> may not be necessary, depending on your preference.
{%- when "Not necessary" -%}
&nbsp; The tolerances on this switch are generally very good, so the use of <a href="/collections/switch-films" target="_blank">switch films</a> is not normally necessary for this product.

{%- when "Highly recommended" -%}
&nbsp; It is not uncommon for this switch to suffer from high variation in fitment between the top and bottom housing. Using <a href="/collections/switch-films" target="_blank">switch films</a> is highly recommended for this product.
{%- endcase -%}
